data.title: What to watch: Chris Brown wants to get back with Rihanna
data.meta_description: Daily entertainment news with what to watch tonight on TV, a viral video on what Chris Brown texted to Rihanna and more.
data.text:
What to watch: 'Shipping Wars' on A&E at 9 p.m. EDT/ 8 p.m. CDT

Tonight is a new episode of "Shipping Wars." Chris and Robbie run into some legal troubles in Arizona, and a coin-operated children's ride is delivered to a boy who just lost his father.

New website: ‘Faust’ Study Questions, www.wsu.edu/~brians/hum_303/faust.html

Have you ever wanted to read “Faust” but haven’t because you were overwhelmed by the text itself? Check out this free study guide, which provides key points to the story and asks questions of you, the reader. Today is the birthday of the author of “Faust,” Johann Wolfgang von Goethe, so give it a shot if it’s on your to-read list.
